me.leoko.advancedgui.utils

Class GuiWallInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.GuiInstance
      • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.GuiWallInstance

  • public class GuiWallInstance
extends GuiInstance
    The GuiWallInstance is a GuiInstance that displays a layout in a ItemFrame grid on a wall.
